Package: fmristore
Type: Package
Title: Efficient Storage of fMRI Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Bradley",
           family = "Buchsbaum",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5891-3515"))
Author: Bradley Buchsbaum [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Bradley Buchsbaum <brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com>
Description: Provides efficient storage and retrieval of functional magnetic resonance 
    imaging (fMRI) data using HDF5 format. The package offers S4 classes and methods 
    for working with dense and sparse representations of 4D neuroimaging data, latent 
    space decompositions, and spatially clustered voxel time series. It includes 
    memory-efficient access patterns for large datasets and integrates with the 
    neuroim2 package for standard neuroimaging data structures.
